data.sign: birth mark on left hand bicep

queries.query: SELECT `u`.`iUserId` AS `u_user_id`,`u`.`app_section` AS `u_app_section`,`u`.`eSmoke` AS `u_Smoke`,`u`.`vUploadDoc` AS `u_UploadDoc`,`u`.`eDrink` AS `u_Drink`,`u`.`e420Friendly` AS `u_420Friendly`,`u`.`dHeight` AS `u_Height`,`u`.`iKids` AS `u_Kids`,`u`.`vBodyType` AS `u_BodyType`,`u`.`eGender` AS `u_Gender`,`u`.`vSign` AS `u_Sign`,`u`.`vReligion` AS `u_Religion`,`u`.`eSexualPrefrence` AS `u_SexualPrefrence`,`u`.`vEducation` AS `u_Education`,`u`.`vProfession` AS `u_Profession`,`u`.`iIncome` AS `u_Income`,`u`.`vImage1` AS `u_Image1`,`u`.`vImage2` AS `u_Image2`,`u`.`vImage3` AS `u_Image3`,`u`.`vImage4` AS `u_Image4`,`u`.`tIntrest` AS `u_Intrest`,`u`.`eMarriageStatus` AS `u_MarriageStatus`,`u`.`vTatoos` AS `u_Tatoos`,`u`.`tTravaledPlaces` AS `u_TravaledPlaces`,`u`.`vTriggers` AS `u_Triggers`,`u`.`tAboutYou` AS `u_AboutYou`,`u`.`tAboutLatePerson` AS `u_AboutLatePerson` FROM `users` AS `u` WHERE `u`.`iUserId` = '215'  LIMIT 1
